            'texto1' => 'The Street Fighter 5 story mode not showed up along with the launch of the game, which left many fans disappointed by the lack of content. However, Capcom announced that the order would come in a future update, totally free for those who already own the game. It now comes in late June with several chapters and different levels of difficulty. We tested the story mode at E3 2016 and you can see the news.',
